        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You lob bombs unerringly, despite obstructions or distance.</p>\n<p>When you throw an alchemical item with the&nbsp;bomb&nbsp;trait, its range increment increases to 60 feet, you reduce any circumstance bonus to the target&rsquo;s AC from cover by 1, and you automatically succeed at the flat check when targeting a&nbsp;<a tabindex=\"0\" title=\"\" role=\"button\" data-trigger=\"focus\" data-toggle=\"popover\" data-boundary=\"window\" data-placement=\"auto\" data-html=\"true\" data-content=\"&lt;p&gt;While you are &lt;em&gt;concealed&lt;/em&gt; from a creature, such as in a thick fog, you are difficult for that creature to see. You can still be observed, but you&rsquo;re tougher to target. A creature that you&rsquo;re &lt;em&gt;concealed&lt;/em&gt; from must succeed at a DC 5 flat check when targeting you with an attack, spell, or other effect.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Area effects aren&rsquo;t subject to this flat check. If the check fails, the attack, spell, or effect doesn&rsquo;t affect you.&lt;/p&gt;\" data-original-title=\"&lt;strong&gt;condition: concealed&lt;/strong&gt;\">concealed</a>&nbsp;creature.</p>",
